- Configurable cache for pages (based on last update to content or theme)
- Configurable time cache for facebook users
- Pass extra variables to pages
- Improve rpm distribution
- Improve server scripts (start, restart, stop)
- CLI
    $ kasije create 'my_site'
    $ kasije create 'my_site' engine=freemarker comp=xml
    $ cd 'my_site'
    $ kasije generate 'new_page'
    $ kasije start
    $ kasije start port=1337
- JS compilation (TypeScript, CoffeScript, ECMASCRIPT 6)
- Scripts by CDN on Admin template
- Loading view on admin pages (also on JS ajax queries)
- Support more formats than XML to pages (eg: JSON)
- Function to compress JS or CSS from templates
